GOAL: - Calculate macros and let the user view their goals/progress by macros
	  - Get web scraping done because of Nutritionix API lacking foods
	  - Clean up the UI


Task listing, organized by user story:

(5) User story 1: As a health-conscious user, I want to be able to calculate the Macronutrients based on personal goals and current weight so that I know exactly what my target daily intake should be. 

Task 1: (5) CREATE A UI FOR THE PROGRESS PAGE WHERE DAYS ARE TRACKED AND DISPLAYED IN A CALCULATOR VIEW
Task 2: (3) MACRO CALCULATOR USING A FORMULA FOR EACH OF THE THREE GOALS
Task 3: (2) UPDATE DAILY GOALS LIMIT BASED ON MACRO CALCULATOR


Total for user story 1: 10 hours

----------

(5) User story 2: As a product tester, I need to be able to see that the search function works with most, if not all, searches.

Task 1: (8) WEB SCRAPING (reverse engineering Safeway's private API)
TASK 2: (5) Create an online database to tore web scraping data.
TASK 3: (3) SYNC THAT DATABASE WITH THE APP FOR IT TO BE WORKING PROPERLY
 

Total for user story 2: 16 hours

----------

(3) User story 3: As a user, I want to be able to select brands and add to my daily diet.

Task 1: (5) Allow the user to custom some items in a seperate page. 

Total for user story 3: 5 hours


